# Frontend Architecture Design: AI-Powered Appraisal System

## 1. Framework Choice

| Decision | Selection | Justification |
|----------|-----------|----------------|
| **Core Framework** | React 18+ (TypeScript) | Component reusability, strong ecosystem, excellent performance for data-heavy dashboards |
| **Build Tool** | Vite | Fast HMR, optimized production builds, modern ESM support |
| **UI Library** | ReactJS | Customizable, accessible components, matches enterprise design requirements |
| **Type Safety** | TypeScript strict mode | Mandatory for role/permission data structures and API contracts |


