9. Accessibility (a11y) Requirements
All interactive elements must be keyboard navigable (Tab, Enter, Escape)

ARIA labels for icon buttons: <Button aria-label="Edit draft">

Color contrast ratio of at least 4.5:1 for text

Focus indicators visible on all interactive elements

Screen reader announcements for loading/error states using aria-live regions

